        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 23. Pleojassa moorei n. sp. Variation in antenna 2 article 5 length and gnathopod 2 propodus length relative to body length in males and females from the type collection (Billie Rocks, Signy Island, South Orkney Islands, 4 March 1965, M. H. Thurston, coll., NHM 1969:768:ca. 430, station no. 13(244)). Specimens illustrated in FIGURE 22 are indicated by an arrow. Regression assumptions failed for all plots." ;
